<p>Mark presented work on electroporation imaging at the <a href="http://2018.ebtt.org/">2018 EBTT workshop</a> in Ljubljana organised by Damijan Miklavčič and Lluis M. Mir. This international workshop is intended both for novices and experts in electroporation, including PhD students, researchers and users.</p>
